definition: to hook/to sew/to crochet/hook/check mark or tick/window catch

sentences.english: Trace hooks can be applied at the entry or exit of any function.

sentences.chinese: 試新文胸時，要收緊中間或鬆開鉤子。

sentences.english: Red fruit, blackcurrants, cherries, raspberry jam.

sentences.english: Closeto nightfall a dolphin took the small hook he had rebaited.

sentences.english: European trailing bramble with red berry like fruits.
